<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 01:22:06 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Kraken 加密货币交易所称犯罪团伙声称有权访问部分客户数据</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-13/kraken-says-criminal-group-claims-access-to-some-customer-data</link><description>Kraken 是世界上最古老的加密货币交易所之一，该交易所表示，它正受到一个声称有权访问某些客户账户信息的犯罪集团的勒索。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iL9LUVY0OPx8/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2026 20:15:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-13/kraken-says-criminal-group-claims-access-to-some-customer-data</guid></item><item><title>Strategy 通过混合证券购买 10 亿美元比特币</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-13/strategy-funds-entire-1-billion-bitcoin-buy-with-hybrid-securities</link><description>自 7 月推出高收益证券以来，Michael Saylor&amp;#39;s Strategy Inc. 首次完全通过出售其“Stretch”永久优先股为其最新每周 10 亿美元的比特币购买提供资金。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i8fRz00ApIV0/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2026 14:37:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-13/strategy-funds-entire-1-billion-bitcoin-buy-with-hybrid-securities</guid></item><item><title>与特朗普相关的世界自由项目面临投资者的反抗</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-12/trump-linked-world-liberty-crypto-project-faces-investor-revolt</link><description>特朗普家族的加密货币企业世界自由金融公司 (World Liberty Financial Inc.) 正面临投资者的反抗，其中包括亿万富翁支持者孙宇晨 (Justin Sun)，他指责该项目秘密建立控制措施，让内部人士冻结代币持有者的资金。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iu_BwazV59dw/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 23:45:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-12/trump-linked-world-liberty-crypto-project-faces-investor-revolt</guid></item></channel></rss>